-> remote connect:
    -> ssh:
        -> install this service
        -> service ssh status
            ( check ssh service active )
        -> service ssh start
            ( start this service )
        -> for connect to remote:
            ssh { user name }@{ ip remote host }

-> file transfer:
    -> ftp:
        -> install ftp
        -> ftp { remote ip or domain name }
            ( open ftp connection to remote system )

        -> get or push:
            -> get from remote:
                -> get { file }
                    ( one file )
                -> -> mget { file1 } ... {fileN}
                    ( several files )

            -> push files to remote:
                -> put { file }
                    ( one file )
                -> mput { file1 } ... {fileN}
                    ( several files )